The collection is dedicated to the global fuel crisis!

The idea came to me at the peak of fuel shortages in my country, when I spent half a day in line at a gas station on hot summer days.  
I noticed people how eagerly they want to fill up their cars and it is desirable to fill their canisters. The fuel acquired a new value, it was a movie in reality. On one of those hot days at a gas station, the idea came to me to portray these events under my creative vision, and express the thirst and need for fuel in an erotic manifestation.
